text: Sowashee Creek is a stream in the U.S. state of Mississippi. Sowashee is a name derived from the Choctaw language meaning "raccoons are there". Variant names are "Siwashee Creek", "Sowwasha Creek", and "Sowwashy Creek". ==References== Category:Rivers of Mississippi Category:Bodies of water of Lauderdale County, Mississippi
title: Sowashee Creek
